{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"1644a4266d","title":"致琼崖部队领导人电","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"b578b69bb3","index":0,"year":1940,"month":3,"day":11,"articleId":"1644a4266d"}],"tags":[{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji14","name":"毛泽东全集第14卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives8/main/mao-quanji/maoquanji14.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji14":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"38f36f0b11","type":"paragraph","text":"致琼崖部队领导人电","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji14","articleId":"1644a4266d"},{"id":"32b8f7e53e","type":"paragraph","text":"（1940年3月11日）应坚决改变过去依赖国民党的方针，不依靠国民觉发询，要自力更生，使部队尽量扩大。并依靠群众，建立游击根据地，打击敌伪。[1]这是毛泽东致广东省琼崖抗日游击独立队感队领导人吃的主要内容。琼坐部队是中国共产党在海南岛领导的，以1927年9月海南岛农民起义队伍为基础组建的。当时叫做广东省球崖抗日游击独立队总队。1947年改编","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji14","articleId":"1644a4266d"}],"page":{"id":"1dab546632","publicationId":"maoquanji14","articleId":"1644a4266d","start":475,"end":475}}}},"__N_SSG":true}